@page "/faq"


<div class="faq-container">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <FaqItem Question="What is Blazor?" Answer="Blazor is a .NET web framework for building client-side web apps with C#." />
    <FaqItem Question="Can I use Blazor instead of React?" Answer="Yes, Blazor allows you to write interactive components in C# without JavaScript." />
    <FaqItem Question="Does Blazor support state management?" Answer="Yes, you can manage state using fields, properties, and cascading parameters." />
    <FaqItem Question="Is Blazor good for production?" Answer="Yes, Blazor Server and Blazor WebAssembly are both production-ready." />
</div>
